{
  "texts": [
    "Profiling and Prediction This domain focuses on employing data-driven approaches to make informed decisions and forecasts regarding students' academic journeys.",
    "It includes using AI to optimise admissions decisions and course scheduling, predict and improve dropout and retention rates, and develop comprehensive student models to evaluate and enhance academic achievement by scrutinising patterns and tendencies in student data.",
    "Intelligent Tutoring Systems (ITS) This domain leverages AI to enrich teaching and learning experiences by providing bespoke instructional interventions.",
    "The systems work by teaching course content, diagnosing students' strengths and weaknesses and offering automated, personalised feedback, curating appropriate learning materials, facilitating meaningful collaboration among learners, and providing insights from the teacher's perspective to improve pedagogical strategies.",
    "Assessment and Evaluation This domain focuses on the potential of AI to automate and enhance the evaluative aspects of the educational process."
  ]
}